Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Strip all telemetry — OpenTelemetry, Sentry, GrowthBook, custom events

Removes or stubs all outbound telemetry endpoints:
- OpenTelemetry/gRPC instrumentation entirely removed
- Sentry initialization and capture calls stubbed
